title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Heinkel He 162 - version 0.9c
description:
In this video we will look at the Heinkel He 162 salamander  which has been released yesterday. The aircraft is still in development phase but you can already fly pretty nice with this aircraft.

0:00 title screen
0:10 External review followed by internal review
04:35 Start the engines
10:31 take off first try
11:57 take off second try
16:32 review default liveries

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/22906/native-project-heinkel-he-162-salamander
